<lb n="0316b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT47p0316b0101" rend="margin-left:1em">在天輪　州州皆見月　處處有光明</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b02" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">後頌</cb:mulu><head>後頌</head>
<lb n="0316b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT47p0316b0301" rend="margin-left:1em">大道通天下　明明幾百州　州州各道
<lb n="0316b04" ed="T"/>路　路路合春秋　迷後三身別　悟來
<lb n="0316b05" ed="T"/>一也休　這般無彼此　莫把結怨讎</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">念佛提綱</cb:mulu><head>念佛提綱</head>
<lb n="0316b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT47p0316b0701" rend="margin-left:1em">本自無蹤無跡　方便與君拈出　有人
<lb n="0316b08" ed="T"/>問我何為　南無阿彌陀佛</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b09" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">念佛心開</cb:mulu><head>念佛心開</head>
<lb n="0316b10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT47p0316b1001"><l>因修三昧念彌陀</l><l>忽覩彌陀心上過</l>
<lb n="0316b11" ed="T"/><l>始覺行行皆寶所</l><l>方知土土悉交羅</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b12" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">禪教相成</cb:mulu><head>禪教相成</head>
<lb n="0316b13" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT47p0316b1301"><l>天台賢首慈恩教</l><l>達磨南山意不殊</l>
<lb n="0316b14" ed="T"/><l>法門頭數無窮盡</l><l>不離毫端絕妙麁</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b15" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">三身體同</cb:mulu><head>三身體同</head>
<lb n="0316b16" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT47p0316b1601"><l>三德祕藏及三身</l><l>舒卷臨機分不分</l>
<lb n="0316b17" ed="T"/><l>處處融通無罣礙</l><l>勿教一向作三人</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">三寶不異</cb:mulu><head>三寶不異</head>
<lb n="0316b19" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT47p0316b1901"><l>佛法僧寶最為真</l><l>豈異而今一點靈</l>
<lb n="0316b20" ed="T"/><l>舉一即三三是一</l><l>莫教錯認定盤星</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b21" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">身土不二</cb:mulu><head>身土不二</head>
<lb n="0316b22" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT47p0316b2201"><l>毘盧即是寂光土</l><l>寂光即是大毘盧</l>
<lb n="0316b23" ed="T"/><l>身土本來無二相</l><l>皇城<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0316001" n="0316001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0316001" n="0316001"/>元<anchor xml:id="end0316001"/>是大京都</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b24" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">心佛無殊</cb:mulu><head>心佛無殊</head>
<lb n="0316b25" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT47p0316b2501"><l>此心即是彌陀佛</l><l>彌陀即是自心源</l>
<lb n="0316b26" ed="T"/><l>皆道蟾光有虧減</l><l>誰信從來日日圓</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0316b27" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">絕跡無相</cb:mulu><head>絕跡無相</head>
<lb n="0316b28" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT47p0316b2801"><l>一念圓明法界周</l><l>免向三祇著劫修</l>
<lb n="0316b29" ed="T"/><l>若也此中明了得</l><l>一點微塵也不留</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb n="0317a" xml:id="T47.1973.0317a" ed="T"/>
